# Admin UI conventions (Vue)

## Stack (locked-in)

- Vue (Vite + TypeScript) + Naive UI

## Module headers

- `*.vue` files: start with `<!-- ... -->` YAML header (see `docs/ai/module-headers.md`)
- `*.ts` files: start with `/* ... */` YAML header

## API interaction (planned)

- Prefer a thin API client wrapper with consistent error handling and correlation headers.
- Never embed secrets in client code; use runtime config and server-side secrets only.

